  bluetooth configuration if requested.

  13 Feb 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> ChangeLog:
  Build cron jobs for periodic call here instead that in baselayout.

  13 Feb 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> ChangeLog:
  Add periodic files.

  13 Feb 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> ChangeLog:
